|
:INFO
Disposing of Lye and Raw Soap Batter
Excess raw soap batter (before 24 hours) is caustic and should not go down a drain \
without dilution. Dilute heavily with water and flush with plenty of running water. \
Small amounts are fine. Do not pour into the garden or compost. Hardened soap scraps

:QUOTE
Nobody who respects lye has been seriously hurt by it. The burns come from \
rushing, skipping gloves once, or assuming a small amount does not matter.

